    <item>
      <title>领先军事研究中心称，俄罗斯在乌克兰损失3000辆坦克后依赖旧库存</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-relying-old-stocks-after-losing-3000-tanks-ukraine-leading-military-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家领先的研究中心周二表示，俄罗斯在入侵乌克兰期间损失了 3000 多辆坦克，相当于其战前的全部现役坦克库存，但仍储备有足够的低质量装甲车供多年替换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-relying-old-stocks-after-losing-3000-tanks-ukraine-leading-military-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 10:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>去年法国葡萄酒和烈酒出口因美国宿醉而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-wine-spirit-exports-fell-last-year-us-hangover-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业组织 FEVS 表示，去年法国葡萄酒和烈酒出口量从新冠疫情后的峰值下降，原因是通货膨胀削弱了消费者需求，而且利润丰厚的美国市场的经销商清理了现有库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-wine-spirit-exports-fell-last-year-us-hangover-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
